N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4119.1 - Conduct

State Regulations

All licensees of the commission are required to conduct
themselves in a forthright, gentlemanly manner at all times while on or near
the premises of a licensed harness race track during the operation of a
licensed harness race meeting. Notes
